# Simon Says Game 🎮

A browser-based **Simon Says memory game** built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.
The game challenges players to remember and repeat an increasing sequence of colors.

---

## 🎯 Game Objective

The goal of the game is to **repeat the color pattern correctly** as it grows longer each level.

* Watch the color sequence carefully
* Repeat the sequence by clicking the buttons
* Each correct round increases the level
* If you press the wrong color, the game ends

Try to achieve the **highest score possible!**

---

## 🚀 Live Demo

Play the game here:

https://thesubhamdash.github.io/WEB_DEVELOPMENT/

---

## 🕹️ How to Play

1. Press **any key** to start the game.
2. The game will highlight a **random color**.
3. Remember the sequence of colors.
4. Click the buttons in the **same order**.
5. Each level adds a new color to the pattern.
6. If you click the wrong color, the **game ends**.

